data.description: Welcome home to 308 Crisfield Ct, Abingdon, MD 21009 – Where Comfort Meets Convenience in a One-Level Haven!  Experience the ease and accessibility of one-level living! This home offers the perfect blend of functionality and style, catering to a lifestyle of convenience. No stairs mean effortless navigation and a seamless flow from room to room.  Calling all home chefs! The heart of this home is a massive, open kitchen that's a dream come true. With ample counter space, modern appliances, and a layout that encourages culinary creativity, this kitchen is poised for both daily living and entertaining.  Talking about entertaining - right off the kitchen, step out the sliders to your brick patio and massive fully fenced backyard. Whether you're hosting a barbecue, enjoying a quiet morning coffee, or letting your furry friends roam freely, this backyard is a versatile retreat.  This home features 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 2 large living rooms, and a massive kitchen-dining room combo. Nestled in the highly sought-after community of Constant Friendship in Abingdon, Maryland, this home is conveniently located near everything your heart could desire - seconds from Walmart, Wegmans, Target, Chick-fil-A, Lowe's, BJ's, and so much more.  Enjoy the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the comfort and convenience of single-level living in this Abingdon gem!
